	   <tr><td colspan=2>Looking for a bit of advice (encouragement?) from higher level clerics here..&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><br>Seeing as were are a pretty Group dependant Class, whats a Cleric to do when there are no groups to be found?  Such as in zones where there are simply TOO few people to even make a group, or when you have spent the last hour and a half spaming &quot;Level ** Cleric Looking for a group, Send Tells&quot;...<br><br>I ask this because this HAPPENED to me last night... there were over 70 people in the zone and I could not find a group to save my life... Soloing the undead got me dead twice.. . (thanks to NON undead Adds).  <br><br>Hands down, that was the most BORING night I have spent in EQ... And I am NOT looking to do that again... Any Advice (yea, I know I am whineing a bit here, but it was a bit frustrating and I am looking for solutions, so that it does not become a reoccuring problem).<br><br>As usual, Thanks in Advance!<br><br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Wed Jan 16 13:03:52 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
