	   <tr><td colspan=2>Solo for a cleric is BORING. sometimes you just can't find a group. What lvl are you? Druids and Shamen can pretty much heal the same as Clerics until either 24 or 29, thats when it gets easier to find groups. At 39 you shouldn't have any problems. <br><br>Solo can be good for building up your defense, which adds to your AC rating.(I was told this by some higher ups and seems to be true). Don't let your defense drop to far behind.<br><br>The only advice I can give is either stick out the solo bit, near a zone line, or start an alternate. Play newbie for a while, then try again with the cleric.<br><br>Heh.. try being a wizard and getting a group, those guys have it tough until they can annihilate stuff and evacuate groups.<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br>Theraun<br><br><br></td></tr>
